{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2939,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":7555,"text":"For any of you who have visited\nor lived in New York City,"},{"time":11221,"text":"these shots might start to look familiar."},{"time":16116,"text":"This is Central Park,"},{"time":17800,"text":"one of the most beautifully designed"},{"time":19536,"text":"public spaces in America."},{"time":22432,"text":"But to anyone who hasn't visited,"},{"time":24934,"text":"these images can't really fully convey."},{"time":28565,"text":"To really understand Central Park,"},{"time":30610,"text":"you have to physically be there."},{"time":33769,"text":"Well, the same is true of the music,"},{"time":37874,"text":"which my brother and I composed and mapped"},{"time":40671,"text":"specifically for Central Park."},{"time":43757,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":48815,"text":"I'd like to talk to you today a little bit about the work"},{"time":51641,"text":"that my brother Hays and I are doing --"},{"time":54798,"text":"That's us there. That's both of us actually â€”"},{"time":58244,"text":"specifically about a concept that we've been\ndeveloping over the last few years,"},{"time":62051,"text":"this idea of location-aware music."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65660,"text":"Now, my brother and I, we're musicians"},{"time":67614,"text":"and music producers."},{"time":69253,"text":"We've been working together since,"},{"time":70889,"text":"well, since we were kids, really."},{"time":72901,"text":"But recently, we've become\nmore and more interested"},{"time":75500,"text":"in projects where art"},{"time":77420,"text":"and technology intersect,"},{"time":80248,"text":"from creating sight-specific audio"},{"time":82475,"text":"and video installation"},{"time":84347,"text":"to engineering interactive concerts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":87349,"text":"But today I want to focus on this concept"},{"time":89996,"text":"of composition for physical space."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93738,"text":"But before I go too much further into that,"},{"time":96187,"text":"let me tell you a little bit about how we got started"},{"time":97900,"text":"with this idea."},{"time":99737,"text":"My brother and I were living in New York City"},{"time":101792,"text":"when the artists Christo and Jeanne-Claude"},{"time":103579,"text":"did their temporary installation, The Gates,"},{"time":105808,"text":"in Central Park."},{"time":107629,"text":"Hundreds of these brightly-colored sculptures"},{"time":109273,"text":"decorated the park for a number of weeks,"},{"time":112475,"text":"and unlike work that's exhibited"},{"time":114407,"text":"in a more neutral space,"},{"time":115955,"text":"like on the walls of a gallery or a museum,"},{"time":119110,"text":"this was work that was really in dialogue"},{"time":121421,"text":"with this place,"},{"time":122801,"text":"and in a lot of ways, The Gates"},{"time":124733,"text":"was really a celebration"},{"time":126189,"text":"of Frederick Olmsted's incredible design."},{"time":128922,"text":"This was an experience that stayed with us"},{"time":131184,"text":"for a long time, and years later,"},{"time":133453,"text":"my brother and I moved back to Washington, D.C.,"},{"time":136278,"text":"and we started to ask the question,"},{"time":138555,"text":"would it be possible,"},{"time":140319,"text":"in the same way that The Gates"},{"time":141760,"text":"responded to the physical layout of the park,"},{"time":144958,"text":"to compose music for a landscape?"},{"time":149800,"text":"Which brought us to this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":152447,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":157369,"text":"On Memorial Day, we released \"The National Mall,\""},{"time":161005,"text":"a location-aware album"},{"time":163493,"text":"released exclusively as a mobile app"},{"time":166210,"text":"that uses the device's built-in GPS functionality"},{"time":169921,"text":"to sonically map the entire park"},{"time":172706,"text":"in our hometown of Washington, D.C."},{"time":178460,"text":"Hundreds of musical segments"},{"time":180481,"text":"are geo-tagged throughout the entire park"},{"time":183742,"text":"so that as a listener traverses the landscape,"},{"time":186586,"text":"a musical score is actually unfolding around them."},{"time":189995,"text":"So this is not a playlist or a list of songs"},{"time":192235,"text":"intended for the park,"},{"time":194790,"text":"but rather an array of distinct melodies and rhythms"},{"time":197786,"text":"that fit together like pieces of a puzzle"},{"time":200083,"text":"and blend seamlessly"},{"time":201646,"text":"based on a listener's chosen trajectory."},{"time":204112,"text":"So think of this as"},{"time":205483,"text":"a choose-your-own-adventure of an album."}]},{"cues":[{"time":208024,"text":"Let's take a closer look."},{"time":209616,"text":"Let's look at one example here."},{"time":211404,"text":"So using the app,"},{"time":213682,"text":"as you make your way towards the grounds"},{"time":215956,"text":"surrounding the Washington Monument,"},{"time":217778,"text":"you hear the sounds of instruments warming up,"},{"time":221989,"text":"which then gives way to the sound of a mellotron"},{"time":224997,"text":"spelling out a very simple melody."},{"time":229759,"text":"This is then joined by the sound of sweeping violins."},{"time":235595,"text":"Keep walking, and a full choir joins in,"},{"time":239992,"text":"until you finally reach the top of the hill"},{"time":242094,"text":"and you're hearing the sound of drums and fireworks"},{"time":244844,"text":"and all sorts of musical craziness,"},{"time":247130,"text":"as if all of these sounds are radiating out"},{"time":249943,"text":"from this giant obelisk that punctuates"},{"time":251783,"text":"the center of the park."},{"time":254712,"text":"But were you to walk in the opposite direction,"},{"time":257501,"text":"this entire sequence happens in reverse."},{"time":262872,"text":"And were you to actually exit\nthe perimeter of the park,"},{"time":266072,"text":"the music would fade to silence,"},{"time":268294,"text":"and the play button would disappear."}]},{"cues":[{"time":271671,"text":"We're sometimes contacted by \npeople in other parts of the world"},{"time":274719,"text":"who can't travel to the United States,"},{"time":276646,"text":"but would like to hear this record."},{"time":278797,"text":"Well, unlike a normal album,"},{"time":281440,"text":"we haven't been able to accommodate this request."},{"time":283728,"text":"When they ask for a C.D. or an MP3 version,"},{"time":286726,"text":"we just can't make that happen,"},{"time":288922,"text":"and the reason is because"},{"time":291100,"text":"this isn't a promotional app"},{"time":293085,"text":"or a game to promote or accompany"},{"time":295534,"text":"the release of a traditional record."},{"time":297819,"text":"In this case, the app is the work itself,"},{"time":301553,"text":"and the architecture of the landscape"},{"time":303436,"text":"is intrinsic to the listening experience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":308079,"text":"Six months later, we did a location-aware album"},{"time":310947,"text":"for Central Park,"},{"time":312488,"text":"a park that is over two times\nthe size of the National Mall,"},{"time":315760,"text":"with music spanning from the Sheep's Meadow"},{"time":318144,"text":"to the Ramble to the Reservoir."}]},{"cues":[{"time":321556,"text":"Currently, my brother and I are working on"},{"time":323559,"text":"projects all over the country,"},{"time":325876,"text":"but last spring we started a project,"},{"time":328124,"text":"here actually at Stanford's"},{"time":329785,"text":"Experimental Media Art Department,"},{"time":332377,"text":"where we're creating our largest\nlocation-aware album to date,"},{"time":335335,"text":"one that will span the entirety of Highway 1"},{"time":337425,"text":"here on the Pacific Coast."}]},{"cues":[{"time":339715,"text":"But what we're doing, integrating GPS with music,"},{"time":343865,"text":"is really just one idea."},{"time":346368,"text":"But it speaks to a larger vision"},{"time":348706,"text":"for a music industry that's sometimes struggled"},{"time":350855,"text":"to find its footing in this digital age,"},{"time":353687,"text":"that they begin to see these new technologies"},{"time":356152,"text":"not simply as ways of adding bells and whistles"},{"time":358397,"text":"to an existing model,"},{"time":360254,"text":"but to dream up entirely new ways"},{"time":361992,"text":"for people to interact with"},{"time":363709,"text":"and experience music."}]},{"cues":[{"time":365451,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":367495,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}